      "id": "airflow_dag_text",
      "x": 1090,
      "y": 235,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 125,
      "text": "Airflow DAG: f1_pipeline_dag.py\n\nSchedule: 0 2 * * 0,1 (Sun+Mon 2am UTC)\n\nTask Graph:\n  detect_rounds → ingest_rounds\n    → dbt_run → trigger_evidence_build\n\nAuto-detects season + latest round\nShort-circuits on non-race weekends\nBackfill mode: manual trigger with\n  mode=backfill, season, start/end round",
      "originalText": "Airflow DAG: f1_pipeline_dag.py\n\nSchedule: 0 2 * * 0,1 (Sun+Mon 2am UTC)\n\nTask Graph:\n  detect_rounds → ingest_rounds\n    → dbt_run → trigger_evidence_build\n\nAuto-detects season + latest round\nShort-circuits on non-race weekends\nBackfill mode: manual trigger with\n  mode=backfill, season, start/end round",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
