    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "evidence_code_text",
      "x": 660,
      "y": 1282,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 155,
      "text": "Evidence Markdown Pattern:\n\n```sql qualifying_h2h\nselect * from snowflake.mart_qualifying_h2h\nwhere season = ${inputs.season.value}\n  and constructor_id =\n      '${inputs.constructor.value}'\n  and driver_1_code || '|' ||\n      driver_2_code =\n      '${inputs.pairing.value}'\n```\n<BarChart data={qualifying_h2h}\n  x=round_label y=gap_ms sort=false\n  seriesColors={{\n    [q[0].d1_code]: '#E10600',\n    [q[0].d2_code]: '#00D2BE' }} />",
      "originalText": "Evidence Markdown Pattern:\n\n```sql qualifying_h2h\nselect * from snowflake.mart_qualifying_h2h\nwhere season = ${inputs.season.value}\n  and constructor_id =\n      '${inputs.constructor.value}'\n  and driver_1_code || '|' ||\n      driver_2_code =\n      '${inputs.pairing.value}'\n```\n<BarChart data={qualifying_h2h}\n  x=round_label y=gap_ms sort=false\n  seriesColors={{\n    [q[0].d1_code]: '#E10600',\n    [q[0].d2_code]: '#00D2BE' }} />",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
